<English>: "My pobyedili! Victory is ours!" poster
"My pobyedili! Victory is ours!" ("We won! Victory is ours!" / "Мы победили! Victory is ours!") poster decal in honor of the 80th anniversary of Victory in Europe Day.
Emblem of the 112th Fighter Squadron
Emblem of the 112th Fighter Squadron "Stingers" of the 180th Fighter Wing of the Ohio Air National Guard stationed at Toledo Air National Guard Base, Ohio.
Emblem of the 159th Fighter Squadron
Emblem of the 159th Fighter Squadron "Boxin' Gators" of the 125th Fighter Wing of the Florida Air National Guard stationed at Jacksonville Air National Guard Base, Florida.
Emblem of the California Air National Guard
Emblem of the California Air National Guard.
"Pobyeda za nami." text
"Pobyeda za nami." ("Victory is ours." / "Победа за нами.") text decal.
"Pobyeda nad Byerlinom" decal
"Pobyeda nad Byerlinom" ("Victory over Berlin" / "Победа над Берлином") decal.
Emblem of the Tèzhong Zuòzhàn Dì 73 Lü

Emblem of the Tèzhong Zuòzhàn Dì 73 Lü "Dōnghai Fēilóng" (73rd Special Operations Brigade "East China Sea Flying Dragons" / 特种作战第73旅 "东海飞龙") of the Chinese People's Liberation Army Special Forces stationed in the city of Zhāngzhōu (漳州), Fújiàn (福建).
Emblem of the Tèzhong Zuòzhàn Dì 84 Lü

Emblem of the Kōngjiàng Bīng Jūn Tèzhǒng Zuòzhàn Dì 4 Lián "Jiān Dāo" (Airborne Corps 4th Special Operations Company "Sharp Knives" / 空降兵军特种作战第4连 "尖刀") of the Chinese People's Liberation Army Airborne Corps.
Emblem of Ṭayeset 107 (1971-2005)

Emblem of Ṭayeset 107 "Ṭayeset 'Aviri Hiznev Hakhtom" (Squadron 107 "Orange Tail Knights Squadron" / "םותכה בלזנה יראבא תסייט" 107 תסייט) of the Israeli Air Force during its operation of F-4 Ḳurnas aircraft from 1971-2005.
